===Etymology===
[[couch]] + [[potato]]; coined by Tom Iacino in 1976 as a pun on "boob tuber" ([[boob tube]] = television, [[tuber]] = potato); trademarked by Robert Armstrong 1976–91

===Noun===
{{en-noun|head=[[couch]] [[potato]]|couch potatoes}}

# A person who [[spend]]s a lot of time [[sitting]] or [[lying]] down, often [[watching]] [[television]], eating [[snack]]s or drinking [[alcohol]].

